high_descs: Turn around and cross the room to face the white table with the bowl and lettuce on it.
Pick the lettuce up from the table.
Turn around and turn to face the fridge on the left.
Put the lettuce in the fridge and close the door and then open the door and take the lettuce out and shut the door again.
Turn around and cross the room to face the white table.
Put the lettuce down on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put chilled lettuce on a table.

high_descs: Turn right and then turn right and go just past the fridge then turn right then a quick left and go past the counter to the table
Pick up the lettuce from the table
Turn left then take a quick left and go to the fridge
Put the lettuce in the fridge to chill then take the lettuce out of the fridge
Turn left then take a quick left and go to the table
Put the lettuce in the center of the table
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled head of lettuce on a table

high_descs: Turn around and walk straight ahead to the white table on the other side of the room.
Pick up the lettuce on the right side of the table.
Turn around and walk left to the fridge.
Place the lettuce on the top shelf of the fridge. Close the door, wait a moment, and take it out again.
Turn around and walk straight ahead to the dining room table.
Place the lettuce on the table right in the center, to the left of the rightmost knife.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled head of lettuce on a table.
